Why Visit the United Kingdom?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>UK is one of the world`s favorite tourist and business destination. The breathtaking English countryside with carpets of greenery everywhere makes Britain a great destination to visit. London being the &quot;World City,&quot; adorned with the charm of the old world, offers some of the most spectacular architectural masterpieces of the world. Not to miss are the popular destinations of the UK that are renowned world over, like Piccadilly Circus, Buckingham palace, the British parliament and the London Eye.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn addition, many people travel to the UK to avail the benefits of medical tourism. These mainly include orthopedic surgery, cosmetic surgery, dentistry and infertility treatment. The visa consultants at Orange global Consultancy are experts in the application procedure to be followed to obtain a Visit visa for such purposes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe UK is among the most popular multicultural destinations of the world. With people from different nationalities living in the same country, more than hundred languages are spoken in London itself. Be it England, Scotland, Wales or Northern Ireland, smorgasbord of places to visit in the UK, leave you spoilt for choice with an array of museums, art galleries and theatres. So, you may be an adventure seeker or an art lover, there is something that the Queen`s world offers to all kinds of travelers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe country is an admired destination to find suitable investors that can aid in the expansion or sponsorship of your business plans that are to be materialized within the UK. Further, as the value of the Pound (&pound;) reaches the never-ending altitude, the profit figures of businesses here are sure to be very promising in comparison to other countries.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHence, you can look forward to either set up a franchise or a branch office of your existing business in the UK or establish an altogether new enterprise there. The country offers joint ventures, co-operative partnership opportunities; multilateral aid opportunities, specific private sector options and many other business alternatives. Thus, it is a perfect blend for immense business opportunities and leisure activities at the same time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut you cannot escape the prerequisite to obtain a visitor visa in order to pay a visit to the UK, no matter if you are a business travel, a pleasure seeker or wish to be in the UK for medical treatment. This allows you to stay in the country for up to 6 months. However, people who are visiting for medical purposes may get their tourist visa extended by getting a LTR (Leave To Remain). A visa consultant from Orange global Consultancy is your best bet to get a visit visa in a smooth way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe understand the tediousness in obtaining a visa and thereby eliminate stress that was otherwise involved in your visa procedure, as our skilled and <strong>experienced UK visit visa</strong> specialists work on your case. We are abreast with the latest guidelines that have been issued by the British High Commission regarding the changes in visa procedure or eligibility criteria for the UK visit visa. With visa guidance and assistance of our maven specialists, you can aim to file your visit visa application with confidence. Fill our <strong>free visa assessment form</strong> and we will get in touch with you shortly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>UK Tourist visa from India &ndash; Explained</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to move to UK for the purpose of travelling then you must apply for the UK Tourist visa for which you can apply for a Standard Visitor visa via online before you can travel to any of the places in the UK. A Standard Visitor visa can amount to you paying an &pound;100 for a time period of 6 months in total.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It takes at least 2 weeks to process a UK Tourist visa from India and in case you want to visit UK on a regular basis then it is best to apply for the long-term Standard Visitor visa. You can even pass across UK to another country with the Standard Visitor visa for UK for which you can apply for the Visitor in Transit visa for &pound;64.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the UK border you might be asked about your qualifications as well as the activities you want to do when in UK.&nbsp;You can even apply for extra time of stay in the UK in case you are coming to the nation to get a medical treatment from India. Many people from India apply for the UK tourist visa to tour the nation, or other recreational or leisurely activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you seek&nbsp;more information about UK Visit Visa or Tourist Visa you can write an email on info@orangeglobalconsultancy.in&nbsp;and one of the most experience immigration consultants will get in touch with you to help you out with your questions and concerns or you can also choose to call us on +91-8336933522.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '', '925621221_org_img1.png', 'https://orangeglobalconsultancy.in/cms.php?type=MTQ1', 1, '2023-12-29 00:36:34'),
(146, 116, 'Schengen Visa', '<div>\r\n<p><strong>Schengen Visa</strong> if granted confers upon non-Schengen country citizens an unrestricted freedom to travel to and through the Schengen area. This arrangement is part of treaty organization that has been planned as symbol of unified Europe. The agreement was ratified by 5 of 10 member states of European Economic Community organization near Schengen in Luxembourg in 1985 and was complimented by a convention to apply the agreement in 1990. These provisions were finally enforced in 1995.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis arrangement paved way for extending unrestricted travel permission through the demarked Schengen area to nationals of Schengen states and traveling foreign citizens.&nbsp; The provisions adopted included negligible or no border monitoring at all. &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe basic element of the laws of this treaty is promoting idea of Schengen states as being part of one nation which permits the travelers to traverse through the length and breadth of the continent in a similar way as one would travel through states of a country.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis treaty was conceptualized and integrated into the mainstream European Union laws and statutes through treaty of Amsterdam in 1997. Currently there are 26 ratifying member states in this arrangement</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Austria</li>\r\n	<li>Belgium</li>\r\n	<li>Czech Republic</li>\r\n	<li>Denmark (excluding Greenland and the Faroe Islands)</li>\r\n	<li>Estonia</li>\r\n	<li>Finland</li>\r\n	<li>France (excluding overseas departments and territories)</li>\r\n	<li>Germany</li>\r\n	<li>Greece</li>\r\n	<li>Hungary</li>\r\n	<li>Iceland</li>\r\n	<li>Italy</li>\r\n	<li>Latvia</li>\r\n	<li>Liechtenstein</li>\r\n	<li>Lithuania</li>\r\n	<li>Luxembourg</li>\r\n	<li>Malta</li>\r\n	<li>Netherlands (excluding Aruba, Cura&ccedil;ao, Sint Maarten and the Caribbean Netherlands)</li>\r\n	<li>Norway (excluding Svalbard)</li>\r\n	<li>Poland</li>\r\n	<li>Portugal</li>\r\n	<li>Slovakia</li>\r\n	<li>Slovenia</li>\r\n	<li>Spain (excluding Ceuta and Melilla)</li>\r\n	<li>Sweden</li>\r\n	<li>Switzerland 26 October 2004</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Out of the 26 members only 4 countries are not European Union members i.e. Iceland, Liechtenstein, Norway and Switzerland and 2 European Union Members United Kingdom and Ireland are not part of the Schengen treaty organization.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll internal borders have been abolished and immigration check posts removed for the visitors holding <strong>Schengen visa</strong> and you would not need to pass though immigration counters at borders of Schengen states if you happen to travel from one Schengen state to another Schengen state.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlthough the internal borders have ceased to exist but because of the uniform laws and provisions being incorporated into the statutes of the Schengen visa laws a non-EEA national must always carry all relevant documents that demonstrate the objective of travel to this region.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe kind of permission under this arrangement can vary on the demonstrated objective of visit by foreign traveler. The usual term of the entry permission granted under this arrangement can not exceed 3 months in given period of 6 years. the tenure of the stay of 3 months is calculated from the date of entry into the country.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Schengen visa</strong> can be single entry permission or multiple entry permission. A single entry arrangement runs continuously from the date of entry into a Schengen state from where the journey is originating i.e. the country which has granted you this travel permit.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMultiple entry permission permits you to depart and arrive back in this territory several times but the cumulative period of all subsequent residence can not go beyond 3 months which is calculated from the date of first entry on basis of such a permission. It is necessary that this period of 3 months residence must be within the 6 months (calculated from the first date of entry on basis of this permission.</p>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Types of Schengen Visa&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>There are four main types of Schengen visa</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>1. Schengen visa Type A</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>This type of a Schengen visa allows the people non-Schengen states to transit via or postpone for their connecting flight in the overseas area of an airport situated in a Schengen nation. It is necessary for those travelling from a non-Schengen nation to another non-Schengen nation and who need to link their flights in the airport of a Schengen nation as a result.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>2. Schengen visa Type B</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>When it comes to the Type B visa of the Schengen visa the travel journey can be lesser than a period of five days which is why it has been replaced by the type &ldquo;C&rdquo; with the condition of &ldquo;transit&rdquo;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>3. Schengen visa Type C</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>This is basically a Schengen visa you can apply in case you are intended for a short stay and is also a very commonly applied one from the above mentioned ones.&nbsp; This is a visa which has the authority to be issued by embassies, consulates, appointed external providers of a nation.&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>The most common kind of Schengen visa is known as the Uniform Schengen Visa under which you can find the Schengen visa classifications of A, B and C and also gives you an airport transit visa which allows you to reside in any nation in the Schengen Zone till a time span of 90 days in a six-month duration. It is a necessity for the citizens of some nations to check this.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Also, keep in mind whether or not you need a category C Schengen visa by getting to go through with the all the criteria for Schengen visa entry. As per the resolution of your travel this category C Schengen visa could be a:</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>1. single-entry visa (&ldquo;1&rdquo; on the visa sticker)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>2. double-entry visa (&ldquo;2&rdquo; on the visa sticker)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>3. multiple-entry visa (&laquo; MULT &raquo; on the visa sticker)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>4. Schengen visa Type D</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>This kind of visa is also known as the type D long-stay Schengen visa and under this visa is it must for any newcomer who wants to study, work or live in a Schengen nation for more than 90 days (up to 1 year).</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Transit permit with a validity of 5 days</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Airport transit permission enables international transit travelers to use transit lounges at international airports of Schengen countries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you seek more information about Schengen visa you can write an email on info@orangeglobalconsultancy.in&nbsp;and one of the most experience immigration consultants will get in touch with you to help you out with your questions and concerns or you can also choose to call us on <strong>+91-8336933522.</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '', '585281851_schengen-visa-from-india.png', 'https://orangeglobalconsultancy.in/cms.php?type=MTQ2', 1, '2023-12-29 00:40:05'),
(147, 117, 'USA Visitor Visa Application Process from India - B1/B2 Tourist Visa', '<div>\r\n<h2>USA Visit or Tourist Visa - Selection Criteria</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tourist or visitor visa is the non-immigrant visa that is issued for temporary visit to the USA. Anyone who wishes to go for a temporary business visit can rely on Orange Global Consultancy visit visa services under B1 visa. Visitors interested in exploring the country or visiting for medical treatment can place their trust in us for approval under B2 visit visa for the USA.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUSA&nbsp;visit visas are issued for a minimum of 3 months and for a maximum of 10 years. Our executives are well versed in USA&nbsp;visit visa issues and are capable to assist you in gaining an extension of your transitory visa to the USA for another six months, if required, based on INS approval, while you are still in USA.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThough the requirements for USA&nbsp;visit visas are not as stringent as the permanent USA immigration but there are a few basic requirements that you need to comply with. Visitor visa applicants are required to show that they qualify under the Immigration and Nationality Act provisions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe law presumes every applicant of visitor visa as a future immigrant. So, most requirements are in relation to outdo this presumption of law. You can check these requirements below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You must mention the purpose of your US&nbsp;trip - business, medical treatment, pleasure or any other.</li>\r\n	<li>You must assure authorities that you plan to stay in US&nbsp;only for a limited or specific period.</li>\r\n	<li>You must also prove that you have many binding ties and your home outside the USA that will ultimately ensure your return to your homeland.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides, all applicants of Tourist&nbsp;visas to US are interviewed at the US Consulate, prior to the final visa grant. Immigration consultants at Orange Global Consultancy prepare you beforehand regarding the expected questions at the time of the interview as well as suggested suitable answers for the same. This assures an almost guaranteed success for US&nbsp;visit visas for our clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from the above-mentioned requirements, there are a few document submission requirements as well. This especially stands true for applicants who are visiting for medical treatment. Medical diagnosis by an authorized doctor, letter from the medical facility or physician from US&nbsp;showing the willingness to cure your ailment along with the expected cost and period for treatment and state of financial responsibility by the sponsor (of an organizations and individuals) are among the most essential documents that needs to be presented.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOrange Global Consultancy&nbsp;<strong>immigration specialists</strong>&nbsp;for US&nbsp;are driven by the zeal to succeed, we thereby help you with obtaining all required documents and in fulfilling all requirements for a smooth US&nbsp;visit visa. Kindly fill our free assessment form to initiate your Tourist&nbsp;visa procedure to the USA at the earliest.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>USA Visit Visa - Application Process</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Orange Global Consultancy officials are well acquainted with&nbsp;<strong>US Tourist&nbsp;visa procedure</strong>. To provide you an overview of the whole procedure, given below is a step-by-step process for the USA visit visa, we sail you through:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Paying the service charge and application fee -</strong>&nbsp;All applicants of non-immigrant visa category are required to deposit an application fee along with the VFS service charge. Officials who are traveling for government business and official purpose of international organizations are exempted from making the payment. We make your fee submissions and forward your applications for non-immigrant visa. This is the non-refundable amount. A visa fee receipt is received at the time of fee submissions that help us to take you to the next step.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Completion of application forms and taking a visa appointment -&nbsp;</strong>Visa fee receipt is generated within two business days of fee submission, after which we arrange for an appointment of visa interview for you. Our able immigration team assists you in filling essential immigration forms accurately. DS-156 is the most important form that is filled at this level, along with DS-157 and DS-158 forms, if applicable in your case. A different procedure is followed for a visa application submission at the U.S. Consulate General, Mumbai. With many of our immigration specialists based in Mumbai, our clients never hesitate in approaching us for any of their visa needs, even if it requires to be submitted in Mumbai as well.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Appearing for the visa interview -</strong>&nbsp;You are then requested to report at the US consulate or embassy, to appear for the interview. Our&nbsp;USA immigration&nbsp;specialists help you prepare for these interviews along with getting all your documents ready so as to avoid any refusals. So, you need not worry about refusals as long as you apply through Orange Global Consultancy. We are always on our toes to utilize our resources to the maximum to straighten out the lumps in the approval of your U.S. Tourist&nbsp;visa. Two stickers of barcode along with the original receipt from the authorized bank where the fee payment is made, one latest passport size photograph, appointment letter (printed) and draft, if required, are some essential things that you must carry at the time of the interview.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Passport returned via courier -&nbsp;</strong>Passport of successful visa applicants are retained by the visa officer for stamping purposes. This is couriered via VFS and is delivered at your postal address within seven days of your interview.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Hence, when you levy the responsibility of your&nbsp;<strong>USA Tourist&nbsp;visa approval</strong>&nbsp;on Orange Global Consultancy, you can almost be sure to set forth on your U.S. vacation soon. To get in touch with us, please fill our&nbsp;free assessment form&nbsp;and we will get back to you shortly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>USA Tourist&nbsp;Visa - Reasons For Refusal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>While there are several reasons for refusal of USA Tourist&nbsp;visas and conditions for approval have been made even more stringent after the 9/11 terrorist attack but you need not bother about having to face any such failure as experienced consultants at Orange Global Consultancy stand by your side in every step of the visa process. Our US immigration specialists are well acquainted with the reasons for refusal of applications and ensure that our clients do not have to be disappointed.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe thereby gear you with useful advice to easily qualify through every step and overcome every hurdle without any hassle and finally get your&nbsp;<strong>USA Tourist&nbsp;visa approval</strong>, easily. Grounds on which visa application is usually refused are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Inability to produce sufficient relevant documents</li>\r\n	<li>Insufficient funds to support one`s own or dependants` expenses</li>\r\n	<li>Criminal record of the applicant</li>\r\n	<li>Disclosure of any essential fact about the applicant, otherwise hidden by them.</li>\r\n	<li>Insufficient proof to provide evidence for residence abroad or strong ties, such as family, employment or any other that ensure your return from U.S. after a temporary stay there.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>However, insufficient information provided in the application form and lack of providing the demanded documents may also cause the return of application and extends your visa procedure but this doesn`t cause the refusal of the applications. At Orange Global Consultancy, we assure that your application gets an approval in the minimum possible time, as our executives make sure that such mistakes do not happen and give their best effort to present your case in a favorable light to the U.S. embassy officials. For a&nbsp;free assessment&nbsp;of your profile for USA visit visa, please fill our assessment form and we will get back to you very soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you seek&nbsp;more information about&nbsp;USA B1/B2 Tourist Visa&nbsp;you can write an email on info@orangeglobalconsultancy.in&nbsp;and one of the most experience immigration consultants will get in touch with you to help you out with your questions and concerns or you can also choose to call us on +91-8336933522.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '', '158350825_download.jpg', 'https://orangeglobalconsultancy.in/cms.php?type=MTQ3', 1, '2023-12-29 00:52:08'),
(148, 118, 'Australian Tourist Visa Application Process and Visit Visa Selection Criteria', '<div>\r\n<h2>Australia Visit Visa - Selection Criteria</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In order to visit Australia, you must qualify through the set eligibility criteria brought out by the Australian government. When your purpose of visit is both authentic and legal, assistance of Australian visit visa consultants at Orange Global Consultancy is all you can ask for. Given below are the parameters on the basis of which your eligibility for Australian visit visa is assessed:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You must be residing at the same place from where your application is filed until a decision is taken on your visa application</li>\r\n	<li>Incase, medical treatment is your reason to apply for transitory visa to Australia, a health insurance is mandatory to cover your expenses</li>\r\n	<li>You must provide proof of funds that are required to support yourself and your dependents during your Australian visit</li>\r\n	<li>You must not owe any debts to the Commonwealth of Australia</li>\r\n	<li>Consent for travel of children below 18 years of age</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Conformity to the given selection criteria along with a positive report of basic security and health check makes you an eligible applicant for visit visa to Australia. Our adept&nbsp;<strong>Australian visit visa experts</strong>&nbsp;conduct a free prior assessment of the profile of all our clients and thereafter extend their useful advice if they stand a chance of obtaining an Australian visit visa based on the current eligibility criteria.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou thereby do not waste your precious money and time only to get a refusal as the end result. However, if the assessment results of our experts believe you to be an eligible applicant; we not only give you the go ahead but also support you at every stage of your Australian visit visa approval till the very end.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Australia Visit Visa - Application Process</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Visit visa for Australia is granted to businessmen, pleasure visitors, international students (for a course of up to three months) and those interested in medical tourism to the country. The usual grant is provided for a period of 3-6 months, depending on your purpose of visit. This grant may be extended up to a period of 12 months. In very exceptional circumstances, an extension beyond a year is granted in Australia for a visit visa holder.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAn understanding of both, requirements of our clients&#39;&nbsp;as well as eligibility criteria of Australia visit visa, allow us to find a midway that stand as the hallmark of the expertise of our Australia visit visa specialists. Given below is the procedure we guide you through to get an Australia visit visa:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>We help you fill the right application form that depends on the purpose of your visit. To avoid any delays or refusals, we scrutinize application forms of all our clients to check for any errors and correct them beforehand.</li>\r\n	<li>Duly filled application forms along with the processing fee and essential documents are attached and sent by us to the Australian embassy in your country.</li>\r\n	<li>Sometimes, you may also be asked to appear for an interview. However, there is nothing to worry about as our experts brief you about the most likely questions that may be asked and what are the best answers that can present you in a positive light.</li>\r\n	<li>X-ray examination is mandatory in a few cases; else a normal medical and security check is sufficient.</li>\r\n	<li>With a clearance at the above-mentioned steps, Australia visit visa is granted to you.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tourist visas to Australia</strong>&nbsp;can be granted for either single entry or multiple entries as well. Let us know what your requirements are and period for which you require a visa and leave the rest onto us.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe relentlessly pursue our passion to deliver the best of our visa knowledge and expertise. To affirm your faith in us and get an Australia visit visa soon, we request you to fill our free assessment form and wait for our quick response to suggest if you stand any chances for approval of this visa or if any other visa program is more suitable for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Australia Visit Visa - Why Are Applications Refused ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>While innumerable refusals are an everyday affair at the Australia High Commission, Orange Global Consultancy never lets its clients have those worrisome lines on their forehead and assure them a smiling face forever with Australian visit visa in their hand in the smoothest and earliest way possible.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHaving handled innumerable successful Australian visit visa cases, we are confident about our command to eliminate the knick-knacks of the visa procedure that may cause refusals. In fact, we are also glad to be of help to cases that have faced refusals already but are keen to re-apply through us. Your previous refusal can be due to careless errors, like incomplete application form, lack of the relevant supporting documents, inability to convince the visa officer that you intend to return to your native country after the purpose of your visit has been achieved, lack of health insurance for those going for medical treatment or any other.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur agile Australia visit visa veterans are well aware of these shortcomings and are perfect in fixing them to get you an Australian visit visa. Though we do not mind if you want us to probe into your refused visa case and reapply on your behalf but to save your money and time, it is best to allow our experts to take charge of your case from the very start.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nReasons of refusal may differ for different applicants but solution remains the same for all, i.e, to contact our ace visit visa specialists for Australia, who provide customized solution after a thorough assessment of every case. To get started with us, kindly fill our&nbsp;<strong>free assessment form</strong>&nbsp;and we will get back to you with an analysis of our immigration experts on your case, very soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you seek&nbsp;more information about&nbsp;<strong>Australia Visit Visa&nbsp;</strong>you can write an email on info@orangeglobalconsultancy.in&nbsp;and one of the most experience immigration consultants will get in touch with you to help you out with your questions and concerns or you can also choose to call us on +91-8336933522.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '', '684650918_org_img1.png', 'https://orangeglobalconsultancy.in/cms.php?type=MTQ4', 1, '2023-12-29 00:58:10');
INSERT INTO `cms` (`id`, `menu_id`, `title`, `description`, `video`, `image`, `url`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES
(149, 119, 'United Kingdom Visitor Visa Application Process and Requirement', '<div>\r\n<h2>UK Visitor Visa - Selection Criteria</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever may be your purpose of transitory visit to the UK, selection criteria remains the same for one and all. Our UK visit visa consultants take charge of prior assessment of your profile to check if you qualify for a UK Visit visa. Based on our initial assessment results, our UK experts suggest you a future course of action and guide eligible UK visitors to brace themselves for the selection criteria to qualify easily for the&nbsp;<strong>UK visit visa</strong>, as given below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You must have a valid travel document, such as a passport.</li>\r\n	<li>You are required to convince the visa officer that you have every intention of returning back, once your purpose is served (within six months, except for medical purposes)</li>\r\n	<li>You are visiting the country for a holiday, on a business trip or for medical treatment.</li>\r\n	<li>You are financially sound to support yourself and your dependent family members during your UK visit, without having to seek help from public funds in the UK and without working there. Proof of funds must be submitted.</li>\r\n	<li>A letter of invitation from the company in the UK or from the residing family members, if applicable.</li>\r\n	<li>In case of medical treatment or business purposes, the relevant documents have to be shown.</li>\r\n	<li>A letter of invitation from the company in UK or from the residing family members.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Citizens of European Union countries are exempted from a visa. A valid passport that supports them is sufficient, in case you are a citizen of one of these countries.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn spite of clearing the above mentioned criteria, you might not be cleared for visa incase of the following:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPioneer&nbsp;<strong>immigration and visa consultants</strong>&nbsp;at Orange Global Consultancy would make it easier for you to understand the nitty-gritty linked with your immigration process.&nbsp;<strong>Contact us</strong>&nbsp;as soon as possible and make your application process a hassle free procedure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn spite of clearing the above mentioned criteria, you might not be cleared for visa incase of the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>If you have a criminal record.</li>\r\n	<li>If you are physical unwell.</li>\r\n	<li>If you are unable to produce the required amount or proof of funds for the UK visit.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in forming a rapport with all our clients as we aid you all through during your&nbsp;<strong>UK Visa Process</strong>. You can be confident about your privacy, as we never tamper with your privacy at any cost.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOrange Global Consultancy visa consultants make it simpler for you to understand the rather confusing criteria based on your purpose of visit. All that needs to be done is to contact us at the earliest through our&nbsp;<strong>free assessment form</strong>&nbsp;and we will get back to you within the next two business days.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>UK Visit Visa - Application Process</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The UK visit visa consultants at Orange Global Consultancy are very meticulous regarding the application procedure. This is because a minor error could lead to a refusal. Our visa advisors are highly skilled in spotting errors and ensure that an impeccable application is submitted. Filing the visit visa application in the right way is the most important step. This would determine the acceptance or refusal of your visa.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVisa specialists at Orange Global Consultancy make the process smooth and easy for its clients. The brief application process to obtain the visit visa for the UK is given below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Your profile is assessed by our experts to check whether or not you qualify for the visa. Based on the assessment, we give you the go ahead in applying for this visa or provide you with other suitable options.</li>\r\n	<li>If we find you qualifying for this program, we help you further to fill the application form and present your profile in the best possible way. We forward this form to the UK visa application centre along with the processing fee and see to it that the relevant supporting documents are attached.</li>\r\n	<li>After your application is accepted, we offer you essential tips for an easy-to-qualify interview with the visa officer. We acquaint you with anticipated interview questions and advise you in preparing appropriate answers so that you qualify through the interview with a confident question-answer session.</li>\r\n	<li>The successful interview grants you the privilege of a visit visa to the UK.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Any negligence in filling or submission of UK visa application can cause your visa request to be rejected. However, for anyone who cannot afford to take chances, team Orange Global Consultancy readily stands for assistance to brief you about the required specifications and clarification of any doubts to ensure a flawless submission of your application.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe processing timelines vary according to the visa office where the application is submitted. Usually, the visa office takes decision on most applications within 2- 4 weeks. Though our maven consultants hasten the processing of your application to the best of their capability, it is recommended that you apply at least three months prior to your date of leaving for the UK as legal formalities may get extended due to unforeseen reasons, in a few cases. To know your eligibility for UK visit visa, please fill our free assessment form and we will get back to you shortly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>UK Visitor Visa - Reasons for Refusal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With an inclination to get you the UK visit visa approval; we take pride in boasting about 99% success rate of our esteemed company. While there is no sure shot escape from rejections, we try our best to minimize all possible errors. You might be applying for your visa for the first time, or the High Commission might have previously rejected your case, we provide you a ray of hope for a brighter tomorrow in the UK.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThough many of you might prefer to apply for the UK visit visa yourself but it certainly is difficult to match the insight of our expert UK visa specialists. We look into all individual aspects on the basis of which UK visa officers assess your profile, including the reasons for refusal of your case, previously.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShrinking from taking expert advise from the very start often leads to unnecessary wastage of time, money and efforts. Not to mention, the frustration and delays that it causes due to unnecessary rejections. Do not be the one to face a declination and make a smart move with Orange Global Consultancy from the start. Allow us to take over your UK visit plans and forward your request for a visa, with no room left for refusal.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSome of the most common reasons for&nbsp;<strong>UK Visit Visa</strong>&nbsp;refusal are mentioned below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Inability to prove your intention of returning to your home country.</li>\r\n	<li>Incomplete application</li>\r\n	<li>Insufficient supporting documents</li>\r\n	<li>Insufficient finances or proof of funds to support yourself and your dependents during the visit.</li>\r\n	<li>If you are found to be a threat to the country.</li>\r\n	<li>If any false information is discovered in your profile</li>\r\n	<li>Inability to provide a valid evidence of a sponsor or a letter of invite from the company in UK, if you are applying for a visit visa for business purposes.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>To ensure that such declinations do not happen, we have a highly experienced team of visa advisors and documentation specialists to check that all your information and documents are in place, before the submission of application. For a hassle free vacation to the United Kingdom, fill our free assessment form at once.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you seek&nbsp;more information about&nbsp;UK Visit Visa or Tourist Visa<strong>&nbsp;</strong>you can write an email on info@orangeglobalconsultancy.in&nbsp;and one of the most experience immigration consultants will get in touch with you to help you out with your questions and concerns or you can also choose to call us on +91-8336933522.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '', '489267137_GOING-to-uk-Ielts-for-UK-Visa-Immigration.png', 'https://orangeglobalconsultancy.in/cms.php?type=MTQ5', 1, '2023-12-29 01:04:16');

